"><code>offsetWidth</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/outerText\"><code>outerText</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/style\"><code>style</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/tabIndex\"><code>tabIndex</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/title\"><code>title</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/attachInternals\"><code>attachInternals()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/blur\"><code>blur()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/click\"><code>click()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/focus\"><code>focus()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/beforeinput_event\"><code>beforeinput</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/change_event\"><code>change</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/copy_event\"><code>copy</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/cut_event\"><code>cut</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drag_event\"><code>drag</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragend_event\"><code>dragend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragenter_event\"><code>dragenter</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragleave_event\"><code>dragleave</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragover_event\"><code>dragover</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/dragstart_event\"><code>dragstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/drop_event\"><code>drop</code></a></li><li><em><code>gotpointercapture</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event\"><code>input</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowhide_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowhide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowshow_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/mscandidatewindowupdate_event\"><code>mscandidatewindowupdate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/paste_event\"><code>paste</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>gotpointercapture</code></strong> イベントは、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/setPointerCapture\"><code>setPointerCapture()</code></a> を使用して要素がポインターをキャプチャしたときに発生します。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n      <td>あり</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n      <td>不可</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\" title=\"ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この例では <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 要素を取得し、<code>gotpointercapture</code> イベントを待ち受けします。それから、<code>pointerdown</code> イベントの要素に対して <code>setPointerCapture()</code> を呼び出します。これが <code>gotpointercapture</code> を起動します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> para <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'p'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\npara<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'gotpointercapture'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'キャプチャされた！'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\npara<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'pointerdown'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  para<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setPointerCapture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pointerId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>ongotpointercapture</code> イベントハンドラープロパティを使用した同じ例</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> para <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'p'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\npara<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">ongotpointercapture</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'キャプチャされた！'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\npara<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'pointerdown'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  para<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setPointerCapture</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pointerId<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/pointerevents/#the-gotpointercapture-event","title":"Pointer Events"}],"query":"api.HTMLElement.gotpointercapture_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLElement.gotpointercapture_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/gotpointercapture_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>関連イベント\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerover_event\"><code>pointerover</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerenter_event\"><code>pointerenter</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerdown_event\"><code>pointerdown</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointermove_event\"><code>pointermove</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointercancel_event\"><code>pointercancel</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerout_event\"><code>pointerout</code></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Element/pointerleave_event\"><code>pointerleave</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a> イベントハンドラープロパティ</li>\n  <li><code>Document</code> を対象とするこのイベント: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document/gotpointercapture_event\"><code>gotpointercapture</code></a> イベント</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"gotpointercapture イベントは、 setPointerCapture() を使用して要素がポインターをキャプチャしたときに発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLElement: gotpointercapture event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmlelement/gotpointercapture_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmlelement/gotpointercapture_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement","title":"HTMLElement"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/gotpointercapture_event","title":"HTMLElement: gotpointercapture イベント"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLElement: gotpointercapture イベント - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}